## git hooks uninstall

Uninstalls Githooks run-wrappers into the current repository.

### Synopsis

Uninstall the Githooks run-wrappers and Git config settings
into the current repository.

```
git hooks uninstall [flags]
```

### Options

```
  -h, --help   help for uninstall
```
